{"tid":1064592,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"分貝驚人！得知抽中車路士，布拉格球員內瘋狂慶祝","createTime":"2019-03-16T16:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T07:59:55.000Z","uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0aae5150fc46240911a3587f7e42ed8e6b02c39","tid":1064592,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"香港時間昨晚歐霸盃抽籤結果出爐，捷克球隊布拉格斯拉維亞遭遇英超豪門車路士。通過電視直播觀看抽籤儀式的隊員激動不已。<br />\n<br />\n結果宣佈那一刻，整個更衣室都沸騰了，分貝直線上竄，高呼著「車路士」。<br />\n<br />\n儘管在紙面實力上遠遠遜色於車路士，但是作為本屆歐霸盃的大黑馬，布拉格斯拉維亞的頑強精神令人印象深刻。16強次回合，他們通過加時賽以4-3戰勝西維爾，從而以6-5的總比數將歐霸盃之王拉下馬。"},{"pid":"f8882f36d2c3d54ccc169f5f64a787448a4acc91","tid":1064592,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"上上簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809c73acdefed5f766e40ca65313e7ef6f56708c","tid":1064592,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"煎豆了"},{"pid":"0f398797304dea41e10104fc8ce6357d480835e4","tid":1064592,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb0442c89467aa7fad66ceb780e4c2b6b1a3196","tid":1064592,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"歐霸贏到西維爾會贏唔到垃圾車？"},{"pid":"9c8b992f1952e9cace6953f25163ae810a99ce1f","tid":1064592,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb0442c89467aa7fad66ceb780e4c2b6b1a3196","tid":1064592,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"歐霸贏到西維爾會贏唔到垃圾車？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}